MEDICARE Chiropractic specialist in East Brunswick NJ

Dr. Michael L Pollard is a Chiropractic Specialist in East Brunswick, New Jersey. He graduated with honors from Life Chiropractic College - West in 1999. Having more than 18 years of diverse experiences, especially in CHIROPRACTIC, Dr. Michael L Pollard affiliates with no hospital, and cooperates with other doctors and specialists in medical group Corrective Care Group Pc. Call Dr. Michael L Pollard on phone number (732) 254-5553 for more information and advises or to book an appointment.




