Services
MICHAEL L POLLARD DC PC practices at 85 N LANSDOWNE AVE SUITE #1, LANSDOWNE, PA  19050. Chiropractors diagnose and treat common spinal misalignments that can occur from lifestyle or injuries causing pain, discomfort and degenerative conditions.MICHAEL L POLLARD DC PC may be able to treat; back pain, sciatica, neck pain, shoulder pain, headaches, sports injuries, and auto accident injuries. To learn more, or to make an appointment with MICHAEL L POLLARD DC PC in LANSDOWNE, PA, please call (610) 626-7300 for more information.




